a.xlink:title:
eya_def_tools.data_models.energy_assessment.EnergyAssessment
Energy assessment details and results.
Attributes: gross_energy_assessment (GrossEnergyAssessment): Details and results for the assessment of gross energy yield. plant_performance_assessment (PlantPerformanceAssessment): Plant performance loss assessment categories including results. net_energy_assessment (NetEnergyAssessment): Details and results for the assessment of net energy yield.

eya_def_tools.data_models.scenario.Scenario
Single unique energy yield assessment scenario.
Attributes: id (Optional[str]): Optional unique identifier of the scenario. Default is None. label (str): Label of the scenario. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the scenario. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the scenario. Default is None. is_main_scenario (Optional[bool]): Whether or not this is the main scenario in the report. Default is None. operational_lifetime_length_years (float): Number of years of project operational lifetime. wind_farms (list[WindFarmConfiguration]): List of all wind farms included in the scenario. turbine_wind_resource_assessment (TurbineWindResourceAssessment): Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations. energy_assessment (EnergyAssessment): Energy assessment details and results, including gross energy, plant performance, net energy and uncertainties.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_farm.WindFarmConfiguration
A collection of wind turbines considered as one unit (plant).
Attributes: id (str): Unique identifier of the wind farm. label (str): Label or name of the wind farm. abbreviation (Optional[str]): Optional abbreviated label of the wind farm. Default is None. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the wind farm. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the wind farm. Default is None. turbines (list[TurbineConfiguration]): List of specifications for constituent turbines. relevance (WindFarmRelevance(StrEnum)): The relevance of the wind farm for the assessment ('internal', 'external' or 'future'). operational_lifetime_start_date (date): Operational lifetime start date of the wind farm (format YYYY-MM-DD). operational_lifetime_end_date (Optional[date]): Operational lifetime end date of the wind farm (format YYYY-MM-DD). Default is None. capacity (float): The total project capacity (in MW), which is the lesser of the maximum permanently transmittable power at the grid connection and the maximum production under typical conditions. restrictions (Optional[list[OperationalRestriction]]): List of operational restrictions at the wind farm level. Default is None.

eya_def_tools.data_models.wind_resource.TurbineWindResourceAssessment
Wind resource assessment at the turbine locations.
Attributes: wind_resource_assessment_id_reference (str): The ID of the wind resource assessment on which the turbine wind resource assessment is based. This must refer to an ID of a wind resource assessment included at the top level of the EYA DEF. The schema requires that a turbine wind resource assessment is based on only one wind resource assessment. description (Optional[str]): Optional description of the turbine wind resource assessment. Default is None. comments (Optional[str]): Optional comments on the turbine wind resource assessment. Default is None. wind_spatial_modelling_processes (list[AssessmentProcessDescription]): Wind spatial modelling processes used in the assessment. results (TurbineWindResourceResults): Results of the wind resource assessment at the turbine location(s). wind_uncertainty_assessment (WindUncertaintyAssessment): Wind related uncertainty assessment categories including results.
